name: Homeworld: Vast Reaches

Coming Q4 2025
Designed with the hardcore player in mind, new challenge levels will add hours of expanded content with upgraded visuals!

In Homeworld: Vast Reaches you play as Fleet Command, controlling your ships in vicious real-time combat against a mysterious new enemy.
